= content_for :body_class, 'portfolio-template'

/!  Begin Page Content
section.hero.d-flex
  .container-lg
    .squiggle.mb-5
    .row.justify-content-start.align-items-center
      .col-md-6.col-lg-6
        h1 Construction Marketing Agency Website
        p.lead
        	| Genie Creates is a marketing agency specializing in the construction industry, helping companies strengthen their brand and digital presence.
		.d-inline.mb-5.mb-md-0
			= link_to 'View Website <i class="fad fa-external-link-alt"></i>'.html_safe, 'https://geniecreates.com/', target: "_blank"
      .col-md-6.col-lg-6
        .row.mb-3
			.col-md-6
				h6 Client
				p Genie Creates
			.col-md-6
				h6 Year
				p 2022 - 2024
        .row.mb-3
			.col-md-6
				h6 Services
				p Website Design, Wordpress Development, Graphic Design
			.col-md-6
				h6 Technologies
				p Figma, Wordpress, HTML, PHP, SCSS, JS
section.portfolio-info#info
	.container-fluid.px-md-0
		.row.justify-content-between.g-0.mx-md-0
			.summary.col-12.col-md-4.position-sticky.d-flex.align-items-center.vh-100.mx-auto.top-0
				.flex-grow-1.py-8.py-md-10
					h2 Project Details
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Problem
					p Genie Creates relied heavily on social media and needed a professional website to better showcase their services, expertise, and positioning within the construction industry.
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Process
					p I designed high-fidelity mockups in Figma and led the design and development of a custom WordPress theme. The site was intentionally kept clean and approachable while staying aligned with the agencyâ€™s vision and branding. The structure focused on clearly presenting services and building credibility with prospective clients.
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Outcome
					p The new website provides Genie Creates with a polished online presence that highlights their expertise and supports client growth beyond social platforms. The result is a professional, easy-to-navigate site that strengthens brand credibility and client trust.

			.col-12.col-md-7
				div.pt-md-10
					= link_to image_path("portfolio/genie/genie-creates-showcase.jpg"), "data-fancybox"=>"gallery", "data-caption"=>"Genie Website" do
						= image_tag "portfolio/genie/genie-creates-showcase.jpg", :class=>"img-fluid w-100 h-auto", :alt=>"Genie"
					= link_to image_path("portfolio/genie/genie-homepage.jpg"), "data-fancybox"=>"gallery", "data-caption"=>"Genie Homepage" do
						= image_tag "portfolio/genie/genie-homepage.jpg", :class=>"img-fluid w-100 h-auto", :alt=>"Genie Homepage"
					= link_to image_path("portfolio/genie/genie-about.jpg"), "data-fancybox"=>"gallery", "data-caption"=>"Genie About Page" do
						= image_tag "portfolio/genie/genie-about.jpg", :class=>"img-fluid w-100 h-auto", :alt=>"Genie About Page"
					= link_to image_path("portfolio/genie/genie-contact.jpg"), "data-fancybox"=>"gallery", "data-caption"=>"Genie Contact Page" do
						= image_tag "portfolio/genie/genie-contact.jpg", :class=>"img-fluid w-100 h-auto", :alt=>"Genie Contact Page"

